WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 22]

01:53.790 --> 01:54.650
It's already dawn,

01:55.350 --> 01:56.540
and we've heard all the stories.

01:56.870 --> 01:58.100
Why aren't they out yet?

02:01.510 --> 02:02.570
They're driving me crazy.

02:04.120 --> 02:04.770
In fact,

02:06.590 --> 02:08.490
there is one other way to help Mu Long.

02:10.150 --> 02:10.660
Say it.

02:14.820 --> 02:16.040
The solution lies inside you.

02:18.040 --> 02:21.130
You mean the Dragon Deity's Power?

02:38.030 --> 02:38.690
That scent...

02:41.280 --> 02:42.220
Master Dragon Deity?

02:46.950 --> 02:48.220
Searing flames, ignite!

03:39.790 --> 03:40.940
You're not Lu Wuyi.

04:00.110 --> 04:00.690
Come with me.

04:01.830 --> 04:02.660
Master Dragon Deity?

04:05.070 --> 04:05.850
It's you?

04:10.070 --> 04:11.570
So you really are helping Lu Wuyi.

04:13.230 --> 04:13.730
Wuyi,

04:16.280 --> 04:16.940
what happened to you?

04:18.390 --> 04:18.940
Wu...

04:19.000 --> 04:19.540
It was him.

04:20.990 --> 04:22.780
He used Word Magic on Mu Long.

04:24.040 --> 04:25.610
He joined forces with Jiu Ying long ago.

04:26.870 --> 04:27.810
I found out,

04:29.310 --> 04:30.540
and when I tried to tell you, Wangyan,

04:31.790 --> 04:33.020
he wounded me.

04:35.840 --> 04:36.460
Ji Ling

04:37.350 --> 04:37.980
hurt you?

04:42.190 --> 04:42.850
Ji,

04:43.870 --> 04:44.580
help me.

04:45.550 --> 04:47.370
I'm afraid that if Wangyan learns the truth,

04:48.310 --> 04:49.140
she'll come to despise me.

04:50.430 --> 04:51.660
I don't want to lose her.

05:04.310 --> 05:05.220
You're not saying anything.

05:05.750 --> 05:06.810
Are you admitting it?

05:11.750 --> 05:13.100
Why did you give me this bracelet?

05:15.750 --> 05:17.170
Bai Ze's Eastern Purple Lightning

05:17.720 --> 05:18.900
can suppress evil.

05:21.190 --> 05:21.900
Wear it,

05:22.350 --> 05:23.460
and it can temporarily suppress

05:23.520 --> 05:24.490
Jiu Ying's spirit fragment.

05:30.080 --> 05:30.810
Is it really meant to suppress

05:30.840 --> 05:32.140
Jiu Ying's spirit fragment?

05:32.520 --> 05:33.610
That bracelet is fake.

05:36.110 --> 05:36.610
Ji Ling,

05:37.280 --> 05:38.340
didn't you say that bracelet

05:38.480 --> 05:39.100
could suppress

05:39.110 --> 05:40.050
Jiu Ying's fragment?

05:40.520 --> 05:41.540
Was it a lie?

05:43.480 --> 05:44.730
If I hadn't lied to him,

05:45.670 --> 05:47.580
how could I have lowered his guard?

05:49.480 --> 05:50.980
You can go kill Chi Wen now.

05:51.920 --> 05:53.490
You really did keep your promise.

05:54.750 --> 05:56.140
Now you can sit

05:57.110 --> 05:58.850
on the Dragon Deity's throne

05:59.840 --> 06:00.780
forever.

06:08.280 --> 06:09.250
I believe Wuyi.

06:11.160 --> 06:11.850
Wangyan...

06:12.640 --> 06:14.050
You've sat on the Dragon Deity's throne too long.

06:14.750 --> 06:15.730
You don't want to give it up,

06:15.990 --> 06:16.460
do you?

06:16.990 --> 06:18.780
As long as the Word Magic on Mu Long isn't lifted,

06:19.400 --> 06:21.020
Han Ba won't hand over the Dragon Deity's Power,

06:22.920 --> 06:24.340
and Wu Shiguang won't be able to become a dragon.

06:25.160 --> 06:26.220
And that means

06:27.350 --> 06:28.370
the throne stays his.

06:29.160 --> 06:31.370
You betrayed your oath to Master Chi Wen.

06:31.960 --> 06:33.410
Didn't you reclaim your demon power too,

06:34.670 --> 06:36.020
betraying your oath just the same?

06:36.600 --> 06:38.050
You have no right to accuse me.

06:40.160 --> 06:41.730
But why did he snatch Mu Long's pendant?

06:42.160 --> 06:43.100
Because Su Jian's memories

06:43.310 --> 06:44.340
are stored inside it.

06:44.920 --> 06:46.100
He wanted to help Jiu Ying

06:46.480 --> 06:47.980
hide something shameful.

06:50.080 --> 06:51.540
It has Jian's memories inside.

06:59.430 --> 07:00.460
Even if you take the pendant, it won't help.

07:00.840 --> 07:01.980
We already know everything.

07:02.600 --> 07:03.410
Lu Wuyi

07:04.600 --> 07:06.490
was created by Jiu Ying,

07:07.670 --> 07:08.220
wasn't she?

07:24.430 --> 07:25.580
It's empty?

07:26.310 --> 07:27.250
The memories are gone.

07:32.430 --> 07:33.250
You lied to me.

07:41.520 --> 07:42.220
So she

07:44.840 --> 07:46.370
took the memories back.

07:47.870 --> 07:48.460
The manuscript!

07:48.640 --> 07:49.780
The first chapter of that manuscript

07:50.190 --> 07:51.490
was Little Pomegranate's story.

07:51.790 --> 07:52.490
The handwriting

07:52.750 --> 07:53.980
was all crooked.

07:54.230 --> 07:55.250
It was really ugly.

07:55.640 --> 07:56.410
But still, I recognized

07:56.430 --> 07:57.370
the words "Little" and "Pomegranate."

07:57.370 --> 07:58.430
[The Great Demon and Little Pomegranate]

07:58.430 --> 07:59.730
That was Su Jian's handwriting.

08:00.640 --> 08:01.930
She wrote the story

08:04.520 --> 08:05.460
of Little Pomegranate.

08:05.780 --> 08:10.900
♪The wind blows by, and memories sway with dreams...♪

08:15.520 --> 08:18.140
Master Dragon Deity returned this to us.

08:18.870 --> 08:19.660
He didn't want it.

08:22.100 --> 08:25.300
♪Shaking the story into something blurred and worn♪

08:25.540 --> 08:27.540
♪I am only♪

08:27.660 --> 08:30.700
♪A murmuring traveler through wind and snow♪

08:31.080 --> 08:32.220
I'll go bring the medicine over.

08:32.900 --> 08:38.180
♪Watching the evening glow turn cold and fade into night♪

08:39.540 --> 08:44.580
♪Watching every stroke and mark spell out reluctance♪

08:46.130 --> 08:49.300
♪Watching spider lilies bloom across the hills♪

08:49.460 --> 08:52.780
♪Watching the one in my dreams send back bitterness♪

08:52.980 --> 08:55.820
♪Watching the corner of your lips stained♪

08:55.900 --> 08:58.620
♪With a touch of dark crimson♪

09:00.220 --> 09:05.900
♪From now on, you'll never grow old♪

09:06.260 --> 09:11.460
♪Even with earth between us, I'll softly sing with you♪

09:13.540 --> 09:16.660
♪In spring, I'll gather a thousand flowers for you♪

09:16.980 --> 09:19.660
♪In winter, I'll boil snow to warm the fading dusk♪

09:20.380 --> 09:25.380
♪Of joy and sorrow, of countless softly lit homes, I'll speak to you♪

09:26.580 --> 09:32.980
♪Brewing the years into a daydream impossible to wake from♪

09:33.340 --> 09:39.940
♪Draining every joy and sorrow, crushing the void within the heart♪

09:40.620 --> 09:43.700
♪The white-haired one looks on through tear-blurred eyes♪

09:44.060 --> 09:48.260
♪Sighing for youth, when words defied the heart♪

09:48.820 --> 09:54.780
♪Whose dream lies buried beneath the cenotaph?♪

09:59.220 --> 10:03.700
♪Heavy snow falls, silver light shimmering through the world♪

10:05.260 --> 10:10.540
♪On the lake of the heart drifts a withered lotus leaf♪

10:10.540 --> 10:11.820
[Nian]

10:11.820 --> 10:14.980
♪A young man sits alone with his back turned♪

10:15.260 --> 10:18.420
♪Flowers bloom around the gravestone♪

10:18.660 --> 10:24.020
♪My beloved, I've grown old keeping watch over you♪

10:25.820 --> 10:31.620
♪From now on, you'll never be alone♪

10:32.020 --> 10:37.740
♪Even across the Bridge of Oblivion, I'll say it to you out loud...♪

10:38.310 --> 10:39.770
So what she wrote was "Nian,"

10:41.670 --> 10:43.370
as in never forgetting.

10:50.190 --> 10:51.700
So whenever the wind stirred the tree,

10:53.310 --> 10:54.650
all it carried

10:56.240 --> 10:57.220
were sighs.

10:59.670 --> 11:01.580
And yet I never had the courage to go up to her.

11:17.070 --> 11:17.610
Don't go.

11:18.000 --> 11:18.820
It's dangerous.

11:27.360 --> 11:28.420
His demon power is leaking out.

11:30.160 --> 11:32.060
To keep another drought from breaking out,

11:32.790 --> 11:34.370
I grant you the Dragon Deity's Power.

11:34.920 --> 11:36.180
It can temporarily stop

11:36.240 --> 11:37.490
your demonic energy from leaking.

11:38.640 --> 11:41.610
But this borrowed power will run out one day.

11:42.400 --> 11:42.940
Wangyan,

11:43.640 --> 11:44.980
Han Ba's mind is in chaos.

11:45.520 --> 11:46.820
He's about to lose control of his demon power.

11:50.430 --> 11:51.460
I won't be able

11:52.120 --> 11:53.530
to see Mu Long finish

11:53.590 --> 11:54.890
her story collection after all.

11:59.360 --> 12:00.730
I hid the Dragon Deity's Power

12:02.430 --> 12:04.460
in the place where I first met Su Jian.

12:06.710 --> 12:07.980
I placed a seal on it.

12:09.000 --> 12:10.610
Only when Mu Long regains consciousness

12:11.400 --> 12:13.060
will it be unsealed.

12:14.880 --> 12:16.180
Please, save Mu Long for me.

12:20.920 --> 12:21.460
I'm sorry

12:22.310 --> 12:23.220
that even at the very end,

12:23.520 --> 12:25.340
I'm still this selfish.

12:29.180 --> 12:31.660
♪How pitiful, how sad...♪

12:36.120 --> 12:36.820
This is for you.

12:37.360 --> 12:38.300
At just over 20,

12:38.670 --> 12:40.650
you're the perfect age for carrying an old man's fan.

12:41.220 --> 12:44.300
♪Just lend me one more tomorrow♪

12:44.620 --> 12:47.460
♪To go back and see my hometown♪

12:47.820 --> 12:50.620
♪Holding all my bitter regrets♪

12:50.780 --> 12:53.500
♪As I drift farther away♪

12:54.020 --> 12:56.940
♪I won't wipe my tears dry♪

12:57.300 --> 13:00.100
♪Afraid the sorrow fades too light♪

13:03.820 --> 13:06.260
♪No more longing♪

13:08.780 --> 13:11.500
♪Forget me not, forget me not♪

13:11.820 --> 13:14.980
♪You and I made a promise♪

13:15.140 --> 13:17.580
♪They laugh at me for going mad♪

13:18.020 --> 13:20.820
♪So what if I have?♪

13:21.460 --> 13:24.420
♪Miss me not, miss me not...♪

13:25.470 --> 13:26.420
I'm coming...

13:28.710 --> 13:29.820
to you.

13:30.580 --> 13:34.460
♪It was never here♪

14:13.710 --> 14:15.460
Because of what you did,

14:16.160 --> 14:17.770
none of this can be undone now.

14:18.470 --> 14:20.100
The memories were long gone from that pendant.

14:20.550 --> 14:22.060
Whether I took it or not,

14:22.590 --> 14:23.850
nothing could have prevented

14:23.850 --> 14:25.940
Han Ba's collapse after learning the truth.

14:26.790 --> 14:28.010
The ending was written from the start.

14:28.670 --> 14:29.850
Blaming me won't change a thing.

14:31.590 --> 14:32.820
Such is fate.

14:34.790 --> 14:36.130
No matter how many times we try,

14:40.790 --> 14:42.180
some things can never be undone.

14:44.670 --> 14:45.490
Some people

14:46.310 --> 14:47.700
are destined to be like two great mountains

14:49.160 --> 14:50.490
separated by an endless plain,

14:51.360 --> 14:52.300
a canyon,

14:53.240 --> 14:55.220
or a distance they can never cross.

14:56.190 --> 14:57.580
They watch over each other from afar,

14:58.950 --> 15:01.220
yet can never take one step or even half a step

15:03.400 --> 15:04.130
toward one another.

15:05.950 --> 15:06.700
Tell me.

15:08.360 --> 15:09.100
Tell me.

15:11.310 --> 15:12.530
What are they waiting for?

15:14.190 --> 15:15.670
What are they waiting for?

15:17.760 --> 15:19.220
They're waiting for a snowfall.

15:20.670 --> 15:21.940
They're waiting for a snowfall.

15:24.160 --> 15:25.420
With just one snowfall,

15:26.310 --> 15:27.890
they can bow to each other from afar

15:28.520 --> 15:29.580
and grow old together.

15:30.760 --> 15:32.180
With just one snowfall,

15:33.160 --> 15:34.980
they can bow to each other from afar

15:35.920 --> 15:37.220
and grow old together.

15:50.120 --> 15:50.610
What,

15:51.470 --> 15:52.180
you don't like it anymore?

15:54.120 --> 15:55.730
It doesn't really go with what I'm wearing today.

16:02.920 --> 16:03.580
Come with me!

16:07.000 --> 16:07.580
Wuyi!

16:14.790 --> 16:16.820
I wonder whether Wu Shiguang and Wangyan

16:17.430 --> 16:18.890
will be able to find Ji Ling and Wuyi.

16:20.470 --> 16:21.340
Right now, only Ji Ling

16:21.360 --> 16:22.220
can wake you.

16:23.310 --> 16:24.530
There's nothing I can do to help.

16:44.070 --> 16:45.730
Su Jian treated me like her older sister,

16:46.280 --> 16:47.370
yet I forgot her.

16:49.360 --> 16:50.420
Ji Ling took Wuyi away

16:50.430 --> 16:51.530
right in front of me,

16:52.550 --> 16:54.010
yet there was nothing I could do.

16:56.950 --> 16:57.890
Do you still think of her

16:58.880 --> 16:59.940
as your little sister?

17:00.190 --> 17:01.530
She is my little sister.

17:06.000 --> 17:07.250
Maybe I can't tell

17:07.250 --> 17:08.420
real memories from fake ones,

17:10.880 --> 17:12.570
but when Jiu Ying held me captive,

17:12.950 --> 17:14.010
it was Lu Wuyi

17:14.190 --> 17:15.290
who risked everything to save me.

17:15.400 --> 17:15.980
Wangyan...

17:17.470 --> 17:18.900
When she looked at me,

17:19.950 --> 17:21.010
the trust and dependence

17:21.840 --> 17:22.490
in her eyes

17:24.270 --> 17:25.460
couldn't have been fake.

17:26.710 --> 17:28.330
The one truly at fault in all this

17:28.670 --> 17:29.490
is Ji Ling.

17:30.120 --> 17:31.900
Wuyi was blinded by love.

17:32.270 --> 17:33.660
That's why she covered for him.

17:36.800 --> 17:37.770
You lied to me.

17:48.270 --> 17:49.090
Whatever the truth is,

17:50.120 --> 17:51.010
we have to find them first,

17:53.470 --> 17:54.770
not only to save Lu Wuyi,

17:55.470 --> 17:57.090
but also to put an end to this drought.

17:58.320 --> 17:59.180
I already have three strands

17:59.180 --> 18:00.570
of the Dragon Deity's Power in me.

18:00.990 --> 18:02.050
Once I get the last one,

18:02.710 --> 18:04.140
I can transform into a dragon and bring rain.

18:10.920 --> 18:12.140
I'll take you to Ji Ling.

18:13.560 --> 18:14.770
I know where he is.

18:17.710 --> 18:18.220
Why?

18:22.670 --> 18:24.140
Because I don't trust Lu Wuyi.

18:48.430 --> 18:48.980
Wu.

18:55.470 --> 18:56.980
Has the blowback from the rewinds gotten worse?

18:59.230 --> 18:59.980
That's none of your concern.

19:11.320 --> 19:11.810
Wu,

19:12.750 --> 19:13.940
we are alone now.

19:15.640 --> 19:16.490
Tell me.

19:17.030 --> 19:18.010
Why did you lie to me?

19:23.160 --> 19:25.140
Since you've lived through countless rewinds,

19:26.230 --> 19:27.570
you must've known Wu Shiguang and the others

19:27.710 --> 19:29.460
learned the truth from the painting,

19:31.190 --> 19:32.730
and that the pendant was no longer important.

19:34.400 --> 19:35.620
And you must've known long ago

19:36.320 --> 19:37.810
that there were no memories left inside it.

19:40.320 --> 19:40.770
Am I right?

19:42.430 --> 19:42.900
Yes.

19:52.470 --> 19:53.050
So

19:55.470 --> 19:56.810
from the very beginning,

19:57.880 --> 20:00.250
this was a trap you carefully laid for me.

20:02.560 --> 20:03.290
Then why did you

20:03.290 --> 20:04.730
trick me into stealing

20:06.230 --> 20:07.570
that pendant for you?

20:12.840 --> 20:14.900
Because you killed my sister.

20:29.320 --> 20:30.490
I killed Wu Wangyan?

20:35.360 --> 20:36.770
Do you know

20:38.800 --> 20:39.940
who matters most to me

20:41.880 --> 20:42.660
in this world?

20:50.800 --> 20:51.620
Wu Wangyan.

20:57.230 --> 20:57.900
That's right.

20:59.800 --> 21:00.750
Even after she learned

21:00.750 --> 21:02.330
that I was a monster created by Jiu Ying,

21:03.920 --> 21:05.660
that all my memories with her

21:06.160 --> 21:07.490
were fabricated,

21:11.430 --> 21:12.380
she still saw me

21:15.400 --> 21:17.460
as her irreplaceable little sister.

21:18.380 --> 21:22.020
♪Little grass, O little grass♪

21:22.460 --> 21:25.860
♪You always hang your head, saying nothing...♪

21:27.600 --> 21:28.140
Wuyi,

21:30.670 --> 21:32.140
don't call yourself a monster.

21:33.710 --> 21:34.360
Don't call yourself

21:34.360 --> 21:35.860
trash that nobody wants.

21:39.510 --> 21:41.050
I don't know what others

21:41.050 --> 21:41.860
can give you.

21:42.990 --> 21:44.050
But what I give you

21:45.470 --> 21:46.250
is my heart.

21:47.400 --> 21:48.220
You will always be

21:48.320 --> 21:49.490
my most beloved little sister.

21:50.100 --> 21:53.500
♪Great tree, O great tree...♪

21:54.670 --> 21:55.700
Those words

21:56.510 --> 21:57.980
were meant for Su Jian,

21:58.470 --> 21:59.730
not for me.

22:00.710 --> 22:01.420
This isn't real.

22:06.270 --> 22:07.090
Then what about this?

22:09.750 --> 22:10.810
Is this fake too?

22:12.470 --> 22:13.330
Listen to me carefully.

22:14.190 --> 22:15.010
I will

22:15.430 --> 22:16.900
say this to you once again.

22:18.840 --> 22:20.380
I will always be by your side.

22:21.140 --> 22:25.700
♪Great tree, O great tree♪

22:25.860 --> 22:29.620
♪Through snow and storm, you bend but breathe♪

22:29.900 --> 22:37.340
♪Let's set out toward the spring sunshine without fear♪

22:37.980 --> 22:41.660
♪Little grass, O little grass♪

22:41.940 --> 22:45.660
♪Rise on tiptoe, climb on bravely...♪

22:46.320 --> 22:47.460
You ruined her promise.

22:48.800 --> 22:49.660
You killed her.

22:50.640 --> 22:51.900
In all the previous rewinds,

22:54.160 --> 22:55.810
you killed her right in front of me.

22:57.700 --> 22:59.700
[First time]

23:06.400 --> 23:08.140
You joined forces with Jiu Ying.

23:09.030 --> 23:10.090
You killed Wangyan

23:10.920 --> 23:12.460
so Wu Shiguang would break down,

23:13.080 --> 23:14.490
giving Jiu Ying the chance

23:14.880 --> 23:16.330
to seize Wu Shiguang's body.

23:17.640 --> 23:18.770
You said I lied to you.

23:19.950 --> 23:20.490
You're right.

23:23.840 --> 23:24.730
I did lie to you.

23:25.950 --> 23:27.900
I was never trapped in the time rewinds.

23:28.950 --> 23:31.380
I chose to start over again and again

23:32.920 --> 23:34.140
so I could stop you.

23:35.920 --> 23:36.810
Too bad

23:37.270 --> 23:38.460
I failed every time.

23:39.470 --> 23:40.090
Wangyan!

23:44.140 --> 23:46.340
[Second rewind]

23:46.560 --> 23:47.050
Wangyan!

23:59.510 --> 24:00.140
- Wangyan! - Wuyi.

24:00.140 --> 24:00.990
[Third rewind]

24:00.990 --> 24:01.770
- What's wrong? - Wangyan,

24:01.990 --> 24:02.700
listen to me.

24:03.080 --> 24:03.900
Ji Ling is going to kill you.

24:04.080 --> 24:04.850
Come with me, now!

24:04.950 --> 24:05.490
Wuyi,

24:05.880 --> 24:06.660
what are you talking about?

24:06.750 --> 24:07.810
- I'm serious. - Nobody...

24:08.120 --> 24:08.620
Wang...

24:09.360 --> 24:10.290
Every single time,

24:10.670 --> 24:12.250
I had to watch my sister...

24:12.510 --> 24:13.050
Wangyan.

24:13.120 --> 24:14.250
...die by your hand.

24:16.030 --> 24:16.620
Wangyan!

24:17.320 --> 24:17.900
Wangyan!

24:17.900 --> 24:20.780
[Fifth rewind]

24:20.780 --> 24:22.230
[Sixth rewind]

24:22.230 --> 24:22.860
Wangyan.

24:24.100 --> 24:31.420
[Seventh rewind]

24:31.420 --> 24:33.980
[Eighth rewind]

24:33.980 --> 24:37.140
[Ninth rewind]

24:37.140 --> 24:39.020
[Tenth rewind]

24:39.020 --> 24:40.740
[Eleventh rewind]

24:40.740 --> 24:44.340
[Twelfth rewind]

24:45.270 --> 24:46.090
Ji Ling...

24:46.100 --> 24:47.860
[Thirteenth rewind]

24:48.270 --> 24:49.530
[Fourteenth rewind]
You killed my sister.

24:49.980 --> 24:51.030
[Fifteenth rewind]

24:51.030 --> 24:52.620
I'll never forgive you.

24:53.500 --> 24:55.540
[Sixteenth rewind]

24:56.080 --> 24:57.140
I hate you.

24:57.140 --> 24:58.820
[Seventeenth rewind]

24:59.190 --> 25:00.420
[Eighteenth rewind]
I hate you!

25:07.780 --> 25:10.180
[Nineteenth rewind]

25:16.080 --> 25:17.130
Again and again, I had to endure

25:17.130 --> 25:18.530
that piercing, bone-deep pain,

25:19.470 --> 25:21.010
and still I couldn't change a thing.

25:23.880 --> 25:24.770
But this time,

25:26.750 --> 25:27.620
I did it.

25:28.840 --> 25:29.860
Wu Shiguang didn't get

25:29.880 --> 25:31.220
the Dragon Deity's Power kept by Han Ba,

25:31.800 --> 25:33.420
and Wangyan learned what you were after.

25:34.270 --> 25:36.220
Everyone has seen your true colors.

25:41.470 --> 25:42.220
Wu,

25:44.470 --> 25:45.420
do you know

25:45.470 --> 25:47.180
why I trusted you so much?

25:48.510 --> 25:49.700
Do you know why

25:50.990 --> 25:52.490
I was willing to do everything you said?

25:56.230 --> 25:56.770
No.

25:59.360 --> 25:59.920
Because...

25:59.920 --> 26:00.770
I don't want to know.

26:11.320 --> 26:12.180
So Wu Wangyan

26:16.400 --> 26:17.660
is the only one you truly care about.

26:22.190 --> 26:23.220
Because she

26:25.360 --> 26:26.810
truly cares about me too.

26:26.950 --> 26:27.860
Don't I care about you?

26:41.470 --> 26:42.140
No matter.

26:43.750 --> 26:44.860
I've grown used to it by now.

26:45.750 --> 26:46.900
The people around me

26:47.840 --> 26:49.220
always end up

26:49.950 --> 26:50.620
leaving me

26:51.920 --> 26:52.940
one by one.

26:55.600 --> 26:56.460
No one ever stays.

26:58.670 --> 27:00.380
Lift the Word Magic from Mu Long.

27:03.400 --> 27:04.290
Even if I die,

27:06.950 --> 27:08.770
I won't undo the Word Magic for you

27:09.640 --> 27:11.090
to let you get the Dragon Deity's Power.

27:15.820 --> 27:17.740
♪Through a thousand old dreams♪

27:20.180 --> 27:22.220
♪Through a thousand shadows♪

27:30.820 --> 27:33.300
♪Don't be sad♪

27:33.300 --> 27:35.020
♪Through every yesterday♪

27:35.100 --> 27:37.620
♪Don't you cry♪

27:37.620 --> 27:39.500
♪Through every memory♪

27:39.580 --> 27:47.020
♪I'll always stay with you♪

27:48.180 --> 27:52.060
♪Like sand slipping through fingers tight♪

27:52.620 --> 27:56.500
♪Your name's the words I long to say♪

27:56.900 --> 28:00.540
♪I call for you, my only one♪

28:01.060 --> 28:08.260
♪You're my everlasting bloom♪

28:22.080 --> 28:23.180
You knew I was here?

28:25.080 --> 28:26.220
Have you forgotten

28:26.880 --> 28:28.010
how I found you in the first place?

28:29.360 --> 28:31.460
Why did you appear outside the Shilin Sect?

28:31.880 --> 28:32.770
I don't know.

28:33.510 --> 28:34.660
I just felt

28:35.230 --> 28:36.900
a voice calling me,

28:37.920 --> 28:39.050
telling me to come here.

28:39.990 --> 28:41.420
All these years later,

28:42.800 --> 28:44.490
that obsession is still in me,

28:47.120 --> 28:47.980
telling me to go find you.

28:49.880 --> 28:51.140
And somehow, I always do.

28:52.710 --> 28:54.090
I wonder if I'll ever be able

28:56.470 --> 28:57.180
to figure out

28:57.190 --> 28:58.420
where that obsession comes from.

28:59.750 --> 29:00.290
Li Jie,

29:01.800 --> 29:02.700
do you blame me

29:04.120 --> 29:05.220
for lying even to you?

29:11.080 --> 29:12.030
Though I don't know

29:12.030 --> 29:13.570
your true intentions,

29:14.510 --> 29:15.460
I have

29:17.030 --> 29:17.660
always known

29:17.660 --> 29:18.730
what kind of person you are.

29:20.120 --> 29:20.860
In all the years

29:21.600 --> 29:22.980
I've stayed by your side,

29:23.880 --> 29:24.730
a lot of the time,

29:25.230 --> 29:27.050
I didn't understand

29:27.560 --> 29:28.700
your choices or intentions.

29:29.920 --> 29:30.770
But I knew

29:33.360 --> 29:35.250
you must've had reasons you couldn't speak of.

29:36.470 --> 29:37.460
I will always be

29:38.160 --> 29:40.660
your shield and your blade.

29:43.360 --> 29:44.460
What do we do now?

29:46.750 --> 29:47.700
They're now

29:47.920 --> 29:48.980
all wary of me.

29:50.360 --> 29:52.050
Bring Mu Long here for me.

29:52.950 --> 29:53.940
I'll find a way

29:54.430 --> 29:55.940
to make Lu Wuyi lift the Word Magic.

29:58.880 --> 29:59.290
Understood.

30:02.080 --> 30:03.090
Be careful.

30:27.400 --> 30:28.700
Give me back my sister!

30:41.400 --> 30:42.660
You're using the Dragon Deity's Power

30:42.670 --> 30:43.420
against me?

30:43.800 --> 30:44.700
I'll go rescue Wuyi.

30:52.510 --> 30:53.660
You're trying to take my ring?

30:54.400 --> 30:56.220
I'm going to use Xiaowei's power inside that ring

30:56.560 --> 30:58.010
to lift the Word Magic on Mu Long.

30:59.120 --> 31:00.730
Like the Twelve Thoughts, the Spirit-Binding Ring

31:01.360 --> 31:01.980
obeys only its master.

31:03.640 --> 31:04.730
Even if you take it, it won't obey you.

31:05.640 --> 31:06.250
Its master?

31:07.470 --> 31:08.940
The ring's true master is Chi Wen,

31:09.670 --> 31:10.250
not you.

31:11.360 --> 31:12.860
The Dragon Deity's Power in me

31:13.120 --> 31:14.380
came from my brother.

31:14.840 --> 31:16.220
I'd like to see if it'll

31:16.950 --> 31:17.660
obey you

31:18.320 --> 31:19.090
over me!

31:26.400 --> 31:27.330
Ji Ling...

31:41.840 --> 31:42.460
Wangyan.

32:27.750 --> 32:28.620
Do you still

32:31.990 --> 32:33.460
see me as your little sister?

32:45.080 --> 32:46.330
No matter what happens,

32:48.640 --> 32:50.940
you will always be my most beloved little sister.

32:52.880 --> 32:53.620
I will

32:56.270 --> 32:57.810
always be by your side.

33:04.270 --> 33:05.860
The Word Magic was cast by Lu Wuyi.

33:06.640 --> 33:07.900
Even if you take the ring, it won't help.

33:08.560 --> 33:09.220
Don't believe him!

33:13.360 --> 33:14.380
Wangyan's Word Magic

33:14.400 --> 33:15.380
is far stronger than mine.

33:15.560 --> 33:17.090
If I had really cast it,

33:17.400 --> 33:18.810
how could she possibly fail to undo it?

33:19.920 --> 33:20.530
Wu Shiguang,

33:21.270 --> 33:22.420
Lu Wuyi somehow gained

33:22.430 --> 33:23.940
the power to rewind time.

33:24.360 --> 33:25.460
Her power

33:25.880 --> 33:27.460
has already surpassed all of ours.

33:27.840 --> 33:28.770
You're sharp enough.

33:29.880 --> 33:30.920
Haven't you noticed

33:30.920 --> 33:31.980
anything strange about her?

33:39.190 --> 33:40.980
I don't know which of you is telling the truth.

33:41.920 --> 33:42.730
But it doesn't matter.

33:43.400 --> 33:44.770
Once I get the Spirit-Binding Ring,

33:45.320 --> 33:46.250
I'll know.

34:03.840 --> 34:04.420
Wangyan,

34:11.270 --> 34:11.940
let's go.

35:00.200 --> 35:01.090
Master Dragon Deity...

35:04.920 --> 35:05.460
You Chi!

35:12.360 --> 35:13.380
Hand over the ring,

35:14.320 --> 35:15.530
or I'll kill him.

35:24.590 --> 35:27.300
Only the ancient divine jade, the Spirit-Storing Jade,

35:27.430 --> 35:28.860
can hold the Dragon Deity's Power.

35:29.510 --> 35:32.090
The Spirit-Storing Jade was split in two by heavenly fire.

35:32.510 --> 35:33.170
One became

35:33.590 --> 35:35.170
the six-eyed butterfly demon's

35:35.200 --> 35:35.940
Spirit-Storing Butterfly.

35:36.760 --> 35:37.530
The other became

35:37.990 --> 35:40.570
the Spirit-Binding Ring worn by the Dragon Deity.

35:49.280 --> 35:49.860
Wuyi!

35:53.760 --> 35:54.900
So it really was Lu Wuyi.

35:57.630 --> 35:58.210
Return.

36:05.880 --> 36:06.740
The Spirit-Binding Ring

36:08.360 --> 36:09.490
refused my summons.

36:10.280 --> 36:11.170
How is that possible?

36:12.470 --> 36:13.260
The ring

36:15.110 --> 36:16.380
has accepted Lu Wuyi as its master.

36:33.990 --> 36:35.460
Where could she have taken Long?

36:38.200 --> 36:39.030
What Lu Wuyi wants

36:39.030 --> 36:40.260
has always been the Dragon Deity's Power.

36:40.760 --> 36:41.530
Han Ba said...

36:41.920 --> 36:43.260
I hid the Dragon Deity's Power

36:44.840 --> 36:45.860
in the place where I

36:45.880 --> 36:46.820
first met Su Jian.

36:50.990 --> 36:51.940
The Wei mansion's weaving workshop.

37:00.880 --> 37:01.300
I...

37:02.070 --> 37:03.460
I want to go home.

37:04.680 --> 37:05.300
Don't be afraid.

37:09.320 --> 37:10.570
You'll be home soon.

37:12.760 --> 37:13.460
The Wei mansion?

37:13.950 --> 37:15.340
Isn't that just an ordinary household?

37:15.470 --> 37:16.900
How could it possibly hide the Dragon Deity's Power?

37:17.280 --> 37:19.050
The giant axle in the workshop

37:19.360 --> 37:20.690
is the core of a Firefluff Tree.

37:21.110 --> 37:23.090
I noticed it the first time I went to the Wei mansion.

37:23.400 --> 37:24.610
Back then, I wondered

37:24.840 --> 37:25.650
why Xiaowei always fled

37:25.720 --> 37:26.860
to the weaving workshop

37:27.200 --> 37:28.260
to escape the Ice Curse.

37:31.280 --> 37:32.530
The Firefluff Tree is of fire.

37:33.110 --> 37:34.740
The Ice Curse can't get close to it.

37:35.840 --> 37:38.030
Han Ba hid the Dragon Deity's Power inside the tree core

37:38.030 --> 37:39.170
and cultivated there

37:39.320 --> 37:40.780
to keep his demonic energy from leaking.

37:41.590 --> 37:42.860
What's a Firefluff Tree?

37:43.280 --> 37:44.380
It sounds pretty incredible.

37:44.800 --> 37:45.820
In remote antiquity,

37:45.920 --> 37:46.820
heaven and earth split apart.

37:47.470 --> 37:49.420
Nuwa sought five-colored stones to mend the sky

37:49.430 --> 37:51.490
and sent the Fox Queen to keep the earth together with four pillars of ice.

37:51.680 --> 37:52.980
Where the Four Ice Pillars stood

37:53.320 --> 37:55.820
grew four divine trees of metal, earth, water, and fire.

37:56.070 --> 37:57.980
The Firefluff Tree was one of them.

38:01.030 --> 38:01.820
Han Ba said

38:02.920 --> 38:04.130
that as soon as Mu Long woke up,

38:05.720 --> 38:06.650
the seal would undo itself.

38:08.590 --> 38:09.050
Oh, no.

38:09.880 --> 38:10.380
Let's go!

38:23.550 --> 38:25.050
Wake up.

38:33.430 --> 38:34.380
Wuyi,

38:35.920 --> 38:37.300
where... where am I?

38:38.070 --> 38:39.090
Where's Mr. Yan?

39:05.280 --> 39:05.860
Kneel.

39:54.280 --> 39:55.170
Drink it.

40:07.280 --> 40:08.130
I know him!

40:08.760 --> 40:10.170
I've seen him at the Dragon Deity Temple!

40:10.550 --> 40:11.650
He's Master Chi Wen!

40:12.150 --> 40:13.690
The Dragon Deity has answered our prayers!

40:14.030 --> 40:15.210
We're saved!

40:15.800 --> 40:17.280
Master Chi Wen!

40:17.280 --> 40:18.030
Master Chi Wen,

40:18.030 --> 40:19.020
please send us rain!

40:19.020 --> 40:19.740
Master Chi Wen,

40:19.800 --> 40:20.860
save us!

40:20.990 --> 40:22.640
You can't just stand by and watch us die!

40:22.640 --> 40:23.780
Master Chi Wen!

40:24.920 --> 40:25.820
Master Chi Wen!

40:27.150 --> 40:28.050
He's not the Dragon Deity.

40:28.110 --> 40:29.650
- He can't help us! - Master Chi Wen...

40:32.030 --> 40:32.860
He's not the Dragon Deity!

40:33.280 --> 40:34.340
He's a fake!

40:34.720 --> 40:35.820
He's a fraud!

40:36.200 --> 40:37.260
You're a fraud!

40:37.630 --> 40:39.420
Why did you lie to us?

40:46.950 --> 40:48.490
Why?

40:51.880 --> 40:52.860
Why can't I

40:52.880 --> 40:54.130
change the ending

40:55.200 --> 40:57.940
after everything I've done?

41:09.320 --> 41:09.980
Why?

41:58.110 --> 41:58.940
Why?

42:00.110 --> 42:01.090
Why?

42:14.510 --> 42:15.260
Ji Ling.

42:16.150 --> 42:16.980
Ji Ling.

42:18.110 --> 42:19.650
Ji Ling, wake up.

42:21.360 --> 42:22.340
Ji Ling.

43:08.620 --> 43:09.780
♪It's your light♪

43:09.980 --> 43:11.860
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

43:12.020 --> 43:15.140
♪That set the night alight♪

43:15.500 --> 43:22.020
♪And lead me through the fight♪

43:23.780 --> 43:25.660
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

43:26.100 --> 43:30.540
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

43:31.340 --> 43:33.020
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

43:33.180 --> 43:38.580
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

43:39.340 --> 43:44.740
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

43:47.060 --> 43:53.100
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

43:54.060 --> 43:56.220
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

43:56.500 --> 44:01.340
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

44:01.700 --> 44:04.020
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

44:04.220 --> 44:09.300
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

44:09.540 --> 44:11.540
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

44:11.820 --> 44:16.180
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

44:17.180 --> 44:24.140
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

44:40.700 --> 44:43.660
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

44:44.740 --> 44:48.140
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

44:48.940 --> 44:51.460
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

44:51.700 --> 44:54.780
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

44:55.180 --> 44:57.500
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

44:58.020 --> 45:02.420
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

45:02.660 --> 45:04.820
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

45:05.220 --> 45:10.180
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

45:10.420 --> 45:11.580
♪It's your light♪

45:11.780 --> 45:13.620
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

45:13.820 --> 45:16.940
♪That set the night alight♪

45:17.700 --> 45:27.140
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
